channel.description: Here Are Some Pics Of Blood-Scape v3 (V1 and V2 are private) Home Area & Starting Outfit [img]http://i346.photobucket.com/albums/p438/AnthonyDJr/0016.png[/img] Skillz Area [img]http://i346.photobucket.com/albums/p438/AnthonyDJr/0004.png[/img] Shops [img]http://i346.photobucket.com/albums/p438/AnthonyDJr/0005.png[/img] Pkbox [img]http://i346.photobucket.com/albums/p438/AnthonyDJr/0006.png[/img] Barrows Minigame [img]http://i346.photobucket.com/albums/p438/AnthonyDJr/0007.png[/img] TeamPK [img]http://i346.photobucket.com/albums/p438/AnthonyDJr/0008.png[/img] Slayer [img]http://i346.photobucket.com/albums/p438/AnthonyDJr/0009.png[/img] Jad [img]http://i346.photobucket.com/albums/p438/AnthonyDJr/0010.png[/img] Clan Wars [img]http://i346.photobucket.com/albums/p438/AnthonyDJr/0012.png[/img] Fishing [img]http://i346.photobucket.com/albums/p438/AnthonyDJr/0013.png[/img] Choose A Portal To Go To PKbox Or Teampk [img]http://i346.photobucket.com/albums/p438/AnthonyDJr/0014.png[/img] And Last Mod+Zone With PK Area [img]http://i346.photobucket.com/albums/p438/AnthonyDJr/0015.png[/img] Places Not Posted: Training, GSMINI Places Still Working On: Training, Shops, Barrows Minigame, TeamPK, Slayer, Clan Wars, Fishing, & Mod+Zone. Reasons: Training: Moving Train Area atm because it was in with the Skilling Area. Shops: Soon To Move Them So Its Not Crowded. Barrows MiniGame: Not Quite Finished Yet. TeamPK: Gonna Make A Smaller But Better One. Slayer: Going To Make It Into A Slayer Lvl Gaining MiniGame. So Its Like When You Get A Certain Slayer Lvl You Can Go To Next Portal. GSMINI: Too Old To See. :cool: Clan Wars: Gonna Upgrade and make It WAY better. Fishing: Gonna Move To A More Decent Spot. Mod+Zone: Going To Move To A Spot Never Before.
